Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,POPP'S RESOLVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:01:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...Is changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the true form of a Dragon Knight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The combined power of Dragon,\NDarkling, and human.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ultimate Combat Form\Nof the Dragon Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That is this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The form known as the Dragonoid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragonoid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What unbelievable pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's been this imposing before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Hadorra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, get into the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm fighting, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!\NYou can sense it, can't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran's overwhelming Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're out of Magic Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're useless here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:02:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp! Don't be stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll support these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Look after Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens to us,\Ntake Dai and run as far as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Fine then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't any of you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare attack the wounded\Nfrom behind?! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I take Dragonoid form,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I become intent only on wiping out\Nany enemy in sight, like a Demon Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This power is too strong\Nfor me to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wounded or whelp,\NI cannot spare any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But can you blame me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You pried into the scar on my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Bagi!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to wipe us out at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't beat him!\NEven if we were at our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,His power is on a whole different level!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's truly a super being with the power\Nof a Dragon and Magic Power of a Darkling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen nothing of my Magic Power yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll erase you all in an instant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with the purification spell\Nonly usable in this form!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,With Doru Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good! We can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Baran! Don't give yourself\Nover to any more violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words mean nothing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I take the form of the Dragonoid...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot turn back until you are all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was far more vivid than a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A vision?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai... Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let Dai and Baran meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, run! Get in the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the one who called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you don't look like me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You look... like a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, this form is not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you take after your mother more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt you can become a Dragonoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Remove that cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell... I can tell!\NYou're not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:08:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That crest on your forehead is proof.\NIt's the unspoken bond between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,While our forms are different,\Nwe are father and son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What can a piece of trash like you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing! I know that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one left who can even stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Popp! Don't challenge Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you attack me in this form,\NI will brutally respond,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,killing you and everyone here\Nexcept for Dino,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how weak that attack may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting Dino has brought out my humanity,\Nbut this is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand Dino over peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally met my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't have him! Father or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never let you have our Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Our Dai"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NWithout Dai, Princess Leona would be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If they hadn't fought Dai, Crocodine\Nand Hyunckel would still be evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And... And me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't met Dai,\NI'd still be running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be a brown-noser.\NAll talk and useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt I'd be worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting Dai changed all of our fates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to Dai that we came this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai is the one who lifts us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For Dai to become the enemy of humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For Dai to disappear from our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you shall die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It-It's no good!\NHe has no humanity left in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I do? I've got no Magic Power\Nor powerful weapons or items!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I can do is punch him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't there anything I can do?!\NThink! Think!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't act,\Nhe's going to take Dai away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master... What would you do, Master Aban?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How would you fight\Nat a time like this, Master?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's still one thing I can do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.55,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}HYADARUKO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NICE-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.60,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEHOMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEAL-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's still one thing I can do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I do that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll end this real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on to that bandana, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it since I was five.\NIt's my trademark.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! Just don't lose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's fighting bare-handed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you insane, Popp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't watch\Nsuch a pathetic suicide attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll shatter him with one blow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,His grip is just a weak Mage's!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got all my life energy\Nfocused in my fingertips!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just let you pull them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Megante!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use Megante, you're sure to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! If I'm unlucky,\NI'll be blown to pieces with nothing left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my master was!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I idolized Master Aban, but this was\None trick I never hoped to copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know if it'll work on Baran!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragonic Aura may be a mighty shield,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but it can be pierced\Nby even greater energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Baran said himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taken that much into account?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I get to die for Dai!\NTo die for the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, I get to die\Nfor the future of all humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could ask for a better reason to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Please, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Don't do it, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This has happened before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get the feeling...\NSomething really, really sad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to... I have to do something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do something, but...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's trying to rip his arm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Leona...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.14,0:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.03,0:14:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Make something up for Maam, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you still have that dumb look\Non your face when I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gone through a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my adventure... ends here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&\c&H00FF00&}Megante!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember it all, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I've been so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Has his memory returned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But the price was all too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! Even after Popp sacrificed himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Does even Megante have no effect on him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Even I would\Ntake damage from Megante.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But, his lack of experience saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as he channeled all of\Nhis life energy and detonated it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,he let his guard down, weakening his grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to fly up and shake him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A meaningless death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Baran, why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan, don't! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop hurting my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dino...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you really have\Nregained your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I completely erased them.\NIt's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really are my dad,\Nwhy are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why take my memories\Nand hurt and kill my friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will wipe out the humans\Nand their allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are my son, you will obey me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right that sometimes\Nhumans can be cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be selfish, they bully,\Nand they can discriminate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But some of them aren't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They can be cowardly, but they\Ntry their best to do what's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's who Popp was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's doing it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to remember such trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll erase your memories again!\NThis time, completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:20:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now forget everything, Dino!\NAnd become my true son!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't forget Popp ever again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never forget him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we do nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Popp sacrificed himself and fought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I can't do anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, gods!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,God of Dragons! Lend us your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't resist!\NYour whole mind could be wiped!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't give in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm Dai, the Hero!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You still resist your father?! You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He struck me while I was shielded\Nby my Dragonic Aura?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai's crest is on his fist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! Impossible! This can't be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In thousands of years\Nof Dragon Knight history{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the light of the crest to appear\Nanywhere other than the forehead...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's never happened before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The human spirit?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this Soara's will?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you face the devil\NWith logic on your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatoe akuma ni seiron kazashite\Nmukatte mitemo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It may just be a rationalization{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sore wa akumade seitouka\Nsashite chigai wa naikamo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, even now I waver{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima mo ima mo yureteiru kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far will we go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wa dokomade yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I heard a voice like an angel's whisper{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.78,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tenshi no sasayaki nimo nita\Nkoe ga kikoeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe it was an imposter's illusion\NIt still rang in my ears{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:26.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hatamata petenshi no mayakashi\Nhitokiwa mimi ni hibiiteita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Exposed to love and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.41,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni hiai ni sarasare nagara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the path strewn with pride{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:34.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hokori mamire michi no tochu{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fleeting moments of cowardice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kiete wa ukabu touhikou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The SOS I held back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:42.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nomikonda SOS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I clenched my trembling fist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:48.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furueru te wo nigirishimeta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That single little promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:53.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tatta hitotsu no chiisana yakusoku ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those trivial little memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}honno sasaina omoidetachi ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're still in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:22:59.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}itsumade tattemo kono mune wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As embers that keep me burning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:03.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kogashi tsuzukeru tomoshibi ni naru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single transparent beam of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitosuji no toumei na hikari ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lights the way before me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.66,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}me no mae wo terashite yuku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is little that I can do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:16.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku ni dekiru koto wa ikutsu mo naisa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just keep on to the future\NI managed to grasp through my faith{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.54,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shinjinuita saki ni te ni shita mirai wo\Nsusunde yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the Dragon Crest on his fist,\NDai unleashes his anger at Baran.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Baran's flames of rage\Nare stoked by his son's retaliation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Teran Kingdom trembles\Nas the Dragon Knights clash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The greatest battle in the world\Nbegins now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.82,0:23:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.33,0:23:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"A Father and Son Clash"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
